HOW TO INSTALL 

step 1: on & off file(s) should be moved to /usr/local/bin/
step 2: cd ~ 
step 3: cd Downloads
step 4: chmod +x /usr/local/bin/on 
step 5: chmod +x /usr/local/bin/off 
step 6: mv off /usr/local/bin 
step 7: mv on /usr/local/bin 



# takes about 3  minutes of your time, but saves alot. 


(commands when installed)
on   #activates 
off  #disables 
(sudo required)

took me about 4 hours, enjoy
